  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b9a\u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9a\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Long line to buy goods at Kinnia Sathosa",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "People are showing more interest in shopping at the Satosa outlet in Kinnia Kachakkodithivi.",
        "Due to the current economic crisis, they are getting it despite waiting in long queues.",
        "Although 1 kg of sugar and 5 kg of rice have been given to each person, people should be given more than this and it is not enough to wait for a very long time, they said."
      ],
